Install Pyinotify

Make sure easy_install is installed:
 sudo apt-get install python-setuptools
Install pyinotify:
 sudo easy_install pyinotify
Check pyinotify is working alright
 python -m pyinotify -v /tmp  # This will run pyinotify and watch /tmp
